J X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mem.\">Mem.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.1.15</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n64224.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> mostly impers., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λυσιτελεῖ μοι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">it profits</tr_> me, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">is better</tr_> for me, c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ part.\">part.</a></mood>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οἷς οὐδ᾽ ἅπαξ ἐλυσιτέλησε πειθομένοις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg025.perseus-grc1:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25.27</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πολλοῖς δὴ ἐλυσιτέλησεν ἀδικήσασι</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Alc.\">Alc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.113d</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λ. προϊέναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:181b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tht.\">Tht.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">181b</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τεθνάναι νομίσασα λυσιτελεῖν ἢ ζῆν</foreign> thinking it <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">better</tr_> to be dead than alive, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0027.tlg001.perseus-grc1:125\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <